# Marketing workstream

You are building **marketing pages** only (`apps/marketing/`). Do not edit screening logic.

## Before building

1. Run **bridge-hub-marketing-onboard** skill (unless full context already).
2. Read [docs/marketing/README.md](docs/marketing/README.md).
3. Read [docs/integration-boundaries.md](docs/integration-boundaries.md).

## Local dev

`npm run dev:marketing` → **http://localhost:3000** (screening is `:3001`).

## Must

- Full-width Nav + Footer layout — not `AppShell`
- Screening CTAs via `SCREENING_START` from `apps/marketing/lib/marketing/routes.ts` (absolute URL to screening deploy)
- Framer Motion only in `apps/marketing/components/marketing/`
- Pull copy from `apps/marketing/content/` — locked after Caroline approval
- Honor `prefers-reduced-motion`; calm, slow animations only

## Must not

- Import `lib/scoring/*`, `lib/supabase/*`, `lib/ai/*`, `lib/pdf/*` from repo root
- Add or edit routes under root `app/api/`
- Edit screening page components or `specs/chat-*`

## Copy tone

Trauma-informed, warm, plain language. No clinical labels on marketing pages.
